<ul>
<li>Another demonstrative pronoun <i>iste</i>, <i>ista</i>, <i>istud</i>, which means 'that of yours', and the intensive pronoun <i>ipse</i>, <i>ipsa</i>, <i>ipsum</i> follow the declension of ille, illa, illud.</li>
</ul>
